column5: Just got back from vacation got out on a few charters... reef fishing in belize    Heres our white bucket haul for the day they were all donated to the locals.  Than got out in the bahamas for some deep sea fishing.   Had one hook up all morning heres the little fella he was snagged in the tail and dead by the time he was boatside.  Fished for a bit at our resort but no luck,  shoulda've brought my rod to the atlantis.   Heres a cool shot our last day from the beach

Glad to hear you enjoyed yourself, heck you even got to go fishing and got a few... Hope that isn't the swimming pool and beach offered to ya on your stay otherwise I would expect you came back with a few less limbs
Cool report love the pics of the sharks.Love to be there but believe it or not I want the weather to get very cold so I can go ice fishin
I know what is this crap I was thinking the fellas would have the hut out when I got back!

Licky pits,  Nice one.  I hear they put corotene in the tap water to enhance tanning success.  Good to see you didn't involuntarily donate a kidney whilst changing your name to corona.  Tu gusta pescar eh? Mi gusta nadar & pescar.  Did you see the Dorado?  Ah, Holidays in the sun  Cheers,

Nice report LMA.   Brings back some great memories when my wife and I spent a week on Ambergris Caye , Belize about 4 years ago.  Unfortunately, I didn't get into any fishing.   I'd love to go back some day.  I liked their exchange rate:   1 US Dollar = 2 Belize Dollars
